| ONNX → DXNN, compile, dxcom | `dx-compiler/CLAUDE.md` |
| Python app, factory, inference | `dx-runtime/dx_app/CLAUDE.md` |
| GStreamer pipeline, stream | `dx-runtime/dx_stream/CLAUDE.md` |

